---
title: Sequence Diagram - Check-out Tamu
---
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor FD as Front Desk
    participant UI as Halaman /occupancy
    participant Act as Server Action checkOut
    participant DB as Supabase
    participant Inv as Modul Billing

    FD->>UI: Pilih reservasi "checked-in"
    UI->>DB: SELECT billing_items, payments WHERE reservation_id = ?
    DB-->>UI: { items[], paid }
    UI-->>FD: Tampilkan total biaya + status bayar
    FD->>UI: Konfirmasi check-out
    UI->>Act: checkOutReservation(reservationId)
    alt Masih ada saldo belum bayar
        Act-->>UI: { error: "Outstanding balance" }
        UI-->>FD: Minta penyelesaian pembayaran
    else Semua lunas
        Act->>DB: UPDATE reservations SET status='checked-out', actual_check_out=NOW()
        DB-->>Act: ok
        Act->>DB: UPDATE rooms SET status='cleaning' WHERE id = ?
        DB-->>Act: ok
        Act->>DB: INSERT INTO housekeeping_tasks (room_id, task_type='checkout-cleaning', status='pending')
        DB-->>Act: ok
        Act->>Inv: Generate invoice final
        Inv->>DB: INSERT INTO invoices (...)
        DB-->>Inv: { invoiceId }
        Act-->>UI: { success: true, invoice }
        UI-->>FD: Tampilkan invoice + status kamar = cleaning
    end
